你做.. <br />\n派到你去忙嘅dept真係有返工冇放工.. OT一日2-3個鐘係基本, 冇OT錢, 佢係補假, 但因為人手長期都唔夠, 基本上都冇乜幾何都俾你拎到假, 提早一個月申請都仲要同班姑娘夾.. <br />\n比同事西面是正常的.. 但班客真係好多都好好人..</blockquote><br />\n利申: 舊年1月係舊翼做過, 做左一個星期就頂唔順quit左.."},{"pid":"c4c008fdf94368879a8c8e279af8e8342e1c436a","tid":398510,"uid":103248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好快就有..<br />\n我call interview, interview同收offer 前後都係2-3星期..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但巴打真係諗清楚先好去做..<br />\n養和個clerk唔係真係做back office嘅野, 聽客電話, 落booking, 收錢, 派文件.. 乜都有得你做.. <br />\n派到你去忙嘅dept真係有返工冇放工.. OT一日2-3個鐘係基本, 冇OT錢, 佢係補假, 但因為人手長期都唔夠, 基本上都冇乜幾何都俾你拎到假, 提早一個月申請都仲要同班姑娘夾.. <br />\n比同事西面是正常的.. 但班客真係好多都好好人..</blockquote><br />\n利申: 舊年1月係舊翼做過, 做左一個星期就頂唔順quit左..</blockquote><br />\n我in咯個dept唔洗對客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打係clerk i定ii?"},{"pid":"d03e6970aae879e97b5190913b0009097e9ca88a","tid":398510,"uid":140631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"見佢都幾高人工 但長期請人 係咪伏得咁緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d4cc95b558aeeffb4be480e8c1cd8c0a3ab75c","tid":398510,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:42:06.000Z","msg":"咩要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e835b34792f14c6af67f4fad20c835264756cb","tid":398510,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好快就有..<br />\n我call interview, interview同收offer 前後都係2-3星期..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但巴打真係諗清楚先好去做..<br />\n養和個clerk唔係真係做back office嘅野, 聽客電話, 落booking, 收錢, 派文件.. 乜都有得你做.. <br />\n派到你去忙嘅dept真係有返工冇放工.. OT一日2-3個鐘係基本, 冇OT錢, 佢係補假, 但因為人手長期都唔夠, 基本上都冇乜幾何都俾你拎到假, 提早一個月申請都仲要同班姑娘夾.. <br />\n比同事西面是正常的.. 但班客真係好多都好好人..</blockquote><br />\n利申: 舊年1月係舊翼做過, 做左一個星期就頂唔順quit左..</blockquote><br />\n我in咯個dept唔洗對客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打係clerk i定ii?</blockquote><br />\n我就咁apply clerk, 之後佢跟資歷派你係 I/II... <br />\n我當時年幾文職經驗佢就當我係 Clerk II..<br />\ninterview時 HR都冇講清楚係要對客, 我都係返工當日先知自己係美其名係clerk, 事實上係reception位.. 仲要on shift..."},{"pid":"335c0221b393bcf5e2683c9a27f8cab850cfdee1","tid":398510,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nForm 5 with 5 passes in HKCEE or above<br />\nMinimum 1 year's clerical experience<br />\nGood command of spoken and written English and Chinese, knowledge of Putonghua is an advantage<br />\nProficiency in using Microsoft applications including Excel, Powerpoint and English &amp; Chinese Word Processing<br />\nCustomer-oriented with good communication skills<br />\nShift duty is required"},{"pid":"c5960c88d3290f2d96c0dfaff16c238bc8c62017","tid":398510,"uid":3080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:29:31.000Z","msg":"咩人工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6b5b6c21450ff9a0d1ffb6e781eb95bc3401c1","tid":398510,"uid":136645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:31:50.000Z","msg":"job duty唔符合事實，告佢商品說明條例啦"},{"pid":"5b1d7926cffb83ee2185db6cbb59fba296bfa9f4","tid":398510,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"申請左幾次都比佢無視 係咪HD FG唔做得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc3b6bcd2e569103180e445a612fd732563dc02","tid":398510,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見佢都幾高人工 但長期請人 係咪伏得咁緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好睇你係咩dept.. 我咁岩派正最忙最多野做嗰個dept, 聽同事同班姑娘講, 好多新人都係1-7日內走, 最長都係留左9-10個月就頂唔順..<br />\n因為冇假放又工時長.. 唔係人人受得..<br />\n我主要都係因為 班同事太西, 工時太長先唔做...<br />\n人工哩樣野 睇下自己眼角係點.. on shift 有機會返六日得 15000X14個月, 但日日都返12個鐘(冇OT補水, OT只補鐘) <br />\n真係你返埋我嗰份..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生好好人, 病人都好好人, 清楚保安姐姐都好好人, 只係班姑娘同clerk西到媽媽聲, 好似前世欠左佢地咁.. 黑口黑面.. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ba485e3c3d14eb3a635a0949c8c639b99c8ed6","tid":398510,"uid":78770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩人工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似岩岩又加左<br />\nClerk  I Entry Salary: HK$19,750 or above<br />\nClerk II Entry Salary: HK$15,350 or above"},{"pid":"5e361f83f9783dfcdf7480c1da84fda9f183285f","tid":398510,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>申請左幾次都比佢無視 係咪HD FG唔做得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係ASSO GRAD+年半clerk exp.入去做..<br />\n我見好多都係哩個程度...<br />\n<br />\n可以試下其他醫院, 因為好多私院都差緊哩個位"},{"pid":"8a8b2c62e46715e497e3d3588b0246341e4d8d54","tid":398510,"uid":88986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見佢都幾高人工 但長期請人 係咪伏得咁緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好睇你係咩dept.. 我咁岩派正最忙最多野做嗰個dept, 聽同事同班姑娘講, 好多新人都係1-7日內走, 最長都係留左9-10個月就頂唔順..<br />\n因為冇假放又工時長.. 唔係人人受得..<br />\n我主要都係因為 班同事太西, 工時太長先唔做...<br />\n人工哩樣野 睇下自己眼角係點.. on shift 有機會返六日得 15000X14個月, 但日日都返12個鐘(冇OT補水, OT只補鐘) <br />\n真係你返埋我嗰份..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生好好人, 病人都好好人, 清楚保安姐姐都好好人, 只係班姑娘同clerk西到媽媽聲, 好似前世欠左佢地咁.. 黑口黑面.. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddde90dd634910e02141b08e1a94b72fda120382","tid":398510,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見佢都幾高人工 但長期請人 係咪伏得咁緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好睇你係咩dept.. 我咁岩派正最忙最多野做嗰個dept, 聽同事同班姑娘講, 好多新人都係1-7日內走, 最長都係留左9-10個月就頂唔順..<br />\n因為冇假放又工時長.. 唔係人人受得..<br />\n我主要都係因為 班同事太西, 工時太長先唔做...<br />\n人工哩樣野 睇下自己眼角係點.. on shift 有機會返六日得 15000X14個月, 但日日都返12個鐘(冇OT補水, OT只補鐘) <br />\n真係你返埋我嗰份..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生好好人, 病人都好好人, 清楚保安姐姐都好好人, 只係班姑娘同clerk西到媽媽聲, 好似前世欠左佢地咁.. 黑口黑面.. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83491ffb42a9a83c9af2c12497bedd9f15957425","tid":398510,"uid":103248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好快就有..<br />\n我call interview, interview同收offer 前後都係2-3星期..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但巴打真係諗清楚先好去做..<br />\n養和個clerk唔係真係做back office嘅野, 聽客電話, 落booking, 收錢, 派文件.. 乜都有得你做.. <br />\n派到你去忙嘅dept真係有返工冇放工.. OT一日2-3個鐘係基本, 冇OT錢, 佢係補假, 但因為人手長期都唔夠, 基本上都冇乜幾何都俾你拎到假, 提早一個月申請都仲要同班姑娘夾.. <br />\n比同事西面是正常的.. 但班客真係好多都好好人..</blockquote><br />\n利申: 舊年1月係舊翼做過, 做左一個星期就頂唔順quit左..</blockquote><br />\n我in咯個dept唔洗對客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打係clerk i定ii?</blockquote><br />\n我就咁apply clerk, 之後佢跟資歷派你係 I/II... <br />\n我當時年幾文職經驗佢就當我係 Clerk II..<br />\ninterview時 HR都冇講清楚係要對客, 我都係返工當日先知自己係美其名係clerk, 事實上係reception位.. 仲要on shift...</blockquote><br />\n我咯份係back office...有講明可能好d<br />\n希望得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4ceaa07599b5116b82de759ee80fceb10398c1","tid":398510,"uid":78770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見佢都幾高人工 但長期請人 係咪伏得咁緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好睇你係咩dept.. 我咁岩派正最忙最多野做嗰個dept, 聽同事同班姑娘講, 好多新人都係1-7日內走, 最長都係留左9-10個月就頂唔順..<br />\n因為冇假放又工時長.. 唔係人人受得..<br />\n我主要都係因為 班同事太西, 工時太長先唔做...<br />\n人工哩樣野 睇下自己眼角係點.. on shift 有機會返六日得 15000X14個月, 但日日都返12個鐘(冇OT補水, OT只補鐘) <br />\n真係你返埋我嗰份..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生好好人, 病人都好好人, 清楚保安姐姐都好好人, 只係班姑娘同clerk西到媽媽聲, 好似前世欠左佢地咁.. 黑口黑面.. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62b143c145c6e145ceb596d90e0b531e2782316","tid":398510,"uid":103248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見佢都幾高人工 但長期請人 係咪伏得咁緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好睇你係咩dept.. 我咁岩派正最忙最多野做嗰個dept, 聽同事同班姑娘講, 好多新人都係1-7日內走, 最長都係留左9-10個月就頂唔順..<br />\n因為冇假放又工時長.. 唔係人人受得..<br />\n我主要都係因為 班同事太西, 工時太長先唔做...<br />\n人工哩樣野 睇下自己眼角係點.. on shift 有機會返六日得 15000X14個月, 但日日都返12個鐘(冇OT補水, OT只補鐘) <br />\n真係你返埋我嗰份..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生好好人, 病人都好好人, 清楚保安姐姐都好好人, 只係班姑娘同clerk西到媽媽聲, 好似前世欠左佢地咁.. 